---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About Astrosyo">
  <main class="about-page">
    <section class="intro">
      <h1>Welcome to Astrosyo</h1>
      <p>At Astrosyo, we’re passionate about making astronomy accessible, engaging, and fun for everyone. Whether you’re a curious beginner or a seasoned skywatcher, our goal is to help you explore the cosmos with confidence.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mission">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>We believe the night sky holds endless wonder. Our mission is to provide honest, in-depth telescope reviews, practical observing tips, and educational articles that inspire you to look up, learn, and discover the universe.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="coverage">
      <h2>What We Cover</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Telescope Reviews</strong> – Unbiased breakdowns of optics, mounts, and accessories.</li>
        <li><strong>How-To Guides</strong> – Step-by-step tutorials for beginners and advanced users alike.</li>
        <li><strong>Astrophotography Tips</strong> – Techniques to capture stunning celestial images.</li>
        <li><strong>Astronomy News</strong> – Updates on discoveries, events, and space missions.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="team">
      <h2>Meet the Team</h2>
      <p>Our crew combines hands-on observing experience, academic research, and a love of teaching. From mirror grinding to mount engineering, each author brings a unique perspective to help you find the right gear and skywatching techniques.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="join">
      <h2>Join Us</h2>
      <p>Subscribe to our newsletter for monthly sky guides, exclusive discounts, and behind-the-scenes content. Connect with us on social media and become a part of the Astrosyo community!</p>
      <a href="/newsletter" class="btn-primary">Subscribe Now</a>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
:root {
  --bg-page: rgb(18, 18, 18);
  --text-color: #ffffff;
  --muted: #aaa;
  --accent-color: #a9b4ff; /* cool blue accent from global.css */
  --card-bg: #1a1a1a;
  --card-radius: 14px;
  --shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  --section-spacing: 2.25rem;
}

/* Page wrapper */
.about-page {
  max-width: 960px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 2.25rem 1rem 3rem;
  color: var(--text-color);
}

/* Section spacing */
.about-page section { margin-bottom: var(--section-spacing); }

/* Intro (no card, just hero-ish text) */
.about-page .intro {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: calc(var(--section-spacing) * 0.9);
}
.intro h1 {
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.4vw, 2.75rem);
  margin: 0 0 .6rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: .2px;
  background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--accent-color), #8882a5);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  background-clip: text;
  color: transparent;
}
.intro p {
  font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.1rem + .2vw, 1.125rem);
  line-height: 1.75;
  color: var(--muted);
  margin: 0 auto;
  max-width: 70ch;
}

/* Card-like sections */
.about-page .mission,
.about-page .coverage,
.about-page .team,
.about-page .join {
  position: relative;
  background:
    radial-gradient(130% 170% at 100% -40%, color-mix(in oklab, var(--accent-color) 14%, transparent) 0%, transparent 60%),
    linear-gradient(180deg, var(--card-bg), #141414);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  border-radius: var(--card-radius);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  padding: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.5rem) clamp(1rem, 3.5vw, 1.75rem);
  overflow: clip;
}

/* Top ribbon accent */
.about-page .mission::before,
.about-page .coverage::before,
.about-page .team::before,
.about-page .join::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute; left: 0; right: 0; top: 0; height: 4px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-color), color-mix(in oklab, var(--accent-color) 40%, #8882a5));
  opacity: .8;
}

/* Section headings */
.about-page .mission h2,
.about-page .coverage h2,
.about-page .team h2,
.about-page .join h2 {
  margin: 0 0 .5rem;
  font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 1.2rem + .6vw, 2rem);
  font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: .2px;
  background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--accent-color), #8882a5);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  background-clip: text;
  color: transparent;
}

/* Body copy */
.about-page .mission p,
.about-page .team p {
  margin: 0;
  color: var(--muted);
  line-height: 1.8;
  font-size: 1rem;
}

/* Coverage list */
.coverage ul {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin: .25rem 0 0;
  display: grid;
  gap: .5rem .75rem;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
}
.coverage li {
  color: var(--muted);
  line-height: 1.7;
  font-size: 1rem;
  position: relative;
  padding-left: 1.25rem;
}
.coverage li::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  left: 0; top: .65em;
  width: .5rem; height: .5rem;
  border-radius: 999px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle at 40% 40%, var(--accent-color), #8882a5);
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(169, 180, 255, 0.15);
}
@media (min-width: 720px) {
  .coverage ul { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
}

/* Primary button */
.btn-primary {
  --cta-accent: var(--accent-color);
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: .5rem;
  padding: .85rem 1.3rem;
  border-radius: 999px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: .2px;
  color: #121212;
  background: linear-gradient(
    180deg,
    color-mix(in oklab, var(--cta-accent) 100%, #000 0%),
    color-mix(in oklab, var(--cta-accent) 85%, #000 15%)
  );
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 22px rgba(0,0,0,0.22), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  transition: transform .18s ease, box-shadow .18s ease, background .18s ease;
}
.btn-primary::after {
  content: "→";
  opacity: .9;
  transform: translateX(0);
  transition: transform .18s ease, opacity .18s ease;
}
.btn-primary:hover {
  transform: translateY(-1px);
  background: linear-gradient(
    180deg,
    color-mix(in oklab, var(--cta-accent) 100%, #000 0%),
    color-mix(in oklab, var(--cta-accent) 95%, #000 5%)
  );
  box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.28);
}
.btn-primary:hover::after { transform: translateX(2px); }
.btn-primary:active { transform: translateY(0); box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); }
.btn-primary:focus-visible {
  outline: none;
  box-shadow:
    0 0 0 3px rgba(255,255,255,0.3),
    0 0 0 6px color-mix(in oklab, var(--cta-accent) 35%, transparent);
}

/* Join section spacing */
.about-page .join .btn-primary { margin-top: .75rem; }

/* Mobile polish */
@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .about-page { padding: 1.75rem 1rem 2.25rem; }
}
</style>